V0505_01_00_00_0.text: Let's see if your skills live up to your reputation.

V0505_01_00_01_0.text: I take no Duelist lightly, no matter where they're from.

V0505_01_00_02_0.text: If you want to reach the top, you'll have to get past me.

V0505_01_00_03_0.text:
In a Duel, words mean nothing.
It's your actions that count.

V0505_01_00_04_0.text: You'll learn that my power transcends dimensions!

V0505_03_00_00_0.text: I know what you're capable of, and this isn't your best.

V0505_03_00_01_0.text: Looks like you're out of options.

V0505_03_00_03_0.text:
I haven't shown my full strength yet.
Not even close.

V0505_03_00_04_0.text: You should've ended me while you still had the chance!

V0505_03_00_05_0.text: I guess you're forcing me to show my true power!

V0505_05_00_00_0.text: I've seen the next evolution of Dueling!

V0505_06_01_02_0.text: I won't let you do that!

V0505_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0505_11_01_00_0.text: I summon my monster in Defense Position!

V0505_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
Xyz Summon!

V0505_11_09_01_0.text: The universal energy swings between darkness and light!

V0505_11_09_01_1.text:
I'll harness the power of this oscillation!
Pendulum Summon!

V0505_15_00_00_0.text: I know exactly what to do!

V0505_16_00_01_0.text: The best you could do wasn't enough.

V0505_21_00_00_1.text: But are you done with this Duel?

V0505_21_00_01_0.text: Where's the fire you showed earlier?

V0505_21_00_03_1.text:
Go ahead and rebuild your strategy.
I'll just tear it down.

V0505_21_00_04_0.text: So this is what you can do when you Duel at your best.

V0505_21_00_05_0.text: I bet you're thinking everything is going to plan.

V0505_28_00_00_0.text: Just because you want to win doesn't mean you can.

V0505_28_00_01_0.text: Your endgame needs to improve, but you have promise.

V0505_28_00_02_0.text: If this was a real battle, you would've lost everything!

V0505_28_00_03_0.text: To be a pro, you can't make even the tiniest mistake.

V0505_29_00_00_0.text:
Well done.
You proved that you're a true competitor.

V0505_29_00_02_0.text: Perhaps you'll exceed even my loftiest expectations.

V0505_29_00_03_0.text: Since you're capable of defeating me, I can use your help.

V0505_29_00_04_1.text: You proved you're worthy of being a Lancer.

V0505_33_00_00_0.text: Observe what makes the strong truly mighty!

V0505_33_00_01_0.text: I've never gone easy on anyone!

V0505_30_00_00_0.text:
I see.
So that's your plan.

V0505_34_00_01_0.text: If you're a real Duelist, let your cards do the talking!

V0505_34_00_03_0.text: Once you start making excuses, you've already lost.

V0505_34_00_04_0.text: My monsters come from a different dimension!

V0505_34_00_05_0.text: The outcome of a Duel is never set in stone.

V0505_34_00_07_0.text: I wish this Duel could last forever, but you'll succumb first.

V0505_34_00_08_0.text: Try to get past my impregnable defense!

V0505_34_00_09_0.text: Playing nice is the quickest way to defeat!

V0505_34_00_10_0.text: Learn what risks are worth taking.

V0505_35_00_00_0.text: A professional must be perfect in all facets of Dueling.

V0505_35_00_01_0.text: Who says there's only one Duelist who can Pendulum Summon?

V0505_36_00_00_0.text: Show me what you can do.

D/D/D Flame King Genghis!
